[48.668346, "o", "\u001b[36m\u001b[1m  ═══ COMMENT & DISCUSSION ANALYSIS ═══\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[37m  AI analyzed 7 comments across 4 defects:\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m  DEF-3901:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    M. Fischer (2025-09-16):\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    \"Confirmed on G20 as well. Same freeze behavior. Suspect the route graph traversal is bl...\"\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    L. Braun (2025-09-22):\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    \"Profiled on bench — recalcRoute() runs synchronously on main thread. 9.2s avg at highwa...\"\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[49.268947, "o", "\u001b[33m  DEF-4512:\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    P. Richter (2025-11-11):\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    \"Map tile loader also runs on main thread. Same pattern as route recalculation — inherit...\"\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[49.268977, "o", "\u001b[90m    T. Weber (2025-11-14):\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    \"Related to DEF-3901? Both are main-thread blocking issues in navigation module ported f...\"\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[49.26905, "o", "\r\n"]
[49.870146, "o", "\u001b[32m\u001b[1m  Key Insights Extracted from Comments:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[32m    ✓ \u001b[39m\u001b[37mMultiple engineers independently identified synchronous execution on main thread\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      Mentioned by 4 engineers | Confidence: High\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[32m    ✓ \u001b[39m\u001b[37mRoot cause traced to iDrive 7 → iDrive 8 migration with no architectural review\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      Mentioned by 3 engineers | Confidence: High\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[49.870218, "o", "\u001b[32m    ✓ \u001b[39m\u001b[37mEngineers linked DEF-3901, DEF-4512, DEF-4822, DEF-4823 as same underlying issue\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      Mentioned by 2 engineers | Confidence: Medium\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[49.87035, "o", "\r\n"]
[51.07144, "o", "\u001b[37m\u001b[1m  Timeline Reconstructed from Comments:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[51.071471, "o", "\u001b[36m    2025-09-16\u001b[39m\u001b[90m → First engineer suspects render thread blocking\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[51.37247, "o", "\u001b[36m    2025-09-22\u001b[39m\u001b[90m → Bench profiling confirms: recalcRoute() = 9.2s synchronous on main thread\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[51.673348, "o", "\u001b[36m    2025-10-01\u001b[39m\u001b[90m → Git blame reveals verbatim copy from iDrive 7 — no migration review\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[51.975106, "o", "\u001b[36m    2025-11-11\u001b[39m\u001b[90m → Pattern recognized in second module (map tile loader)\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[52.275587, "o", "\u001b[36m    2025-11-22\u001b[39m\u001b[90m → Fourth defect filed — engineers converge on same root cause independently\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[52.57631, "o", "\r\n"]
[54.578502, "o", "\u001b[36m\u001b[1m  ═══ FIVE-WHYS ANALYSIS ═══\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[54.578534, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[33m\u001b[1m► Why #1: \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[37mWhy does the navigation system freeze during route recalculation?\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[55.179326, "o", "  \u001b[90m  Answer: The route recalculation algorithm runs on the main UI thread, blocking all rendering and input handling for 8-12 seconds.\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[55.179352, "o", "\r\n"]
[56.380995, "o", "    \u001b[33m\u001b[1m↳ Why #2: \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[37mWhy does route recalculation run on the main UI thread?\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[56.981098, "o", "    \u001b[90m  Answer: The route engine was designed as a synchronous module in iDrive 7. When ported to iDrive 8, the async wrapper was not implemented due to schedule pressure.\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[58.182571, "o", "      \u001b[33m\u001b[1m↳ Why #3: \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[37mWhy was the async wrapper not implemented during the iDrive 8 migration?\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[58.783321, "o", "      \u001b[90m  Answer: The navigation module was classified as \"low-change\" during migration planning. No architectural review was performed — it was a direct code port.\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[58.783838, "o", "\r\n"]
[59.983795, "o", "        \u001b[33m\u001b[1m↳ Why #4: \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[37mWhy was no architectural review performed for the navigation module?\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[60.585871, "o", "        \u001b[90m  Answer: The migration review process only flagged modules with API signature changes. The route engine API remained unchanged, so it was auto-approved.\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[60.585905, "o", "\r\n"]
[61.788953, "o", "          \u001b[33m\u001b[1m↳ Why #5: \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[37mWhy does the review process only check API signatures and not runtime behavior?\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[62.390862, "o", "          \u001b[90m  Answer: The migration review checklist was designed for backend services and does not include performance profiling or threading model validation for embedded HMI components.\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[62.390891, "o", "\r\n"]
[63.592791, "o", "\u001b[31m\u001b[1m  ★ Root Cause Identified at Level 5:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    Migration review process lacks threading model and performance\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m    validation for embedded HMI components.\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[65.594114, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m  ═══ FISHBONE (ISHIKAWA) DIAGRAM ═══\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[65.59416, "o", "\u001b[37m                          NAVIGATION ROUTE ENGINE FREEZE\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[37m                                      │\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[33m    PEOPLE\u001b[39m\u001b[90m ─────────────────────┐\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • Migration team lacked embedded HMI expertise\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • No performance engineer assigned to navigation module\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[66.194401, "o", "\u001b[90m                              ┌─────────────────────── \u001b[39m\u001b[33mPROCESS\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • Migration review checklist missing threading model vali...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • No load testing for route recalculation under high-spee...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • \"Low-change\" classification bypasses architectural review\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[66.795419, "o", "\u001b[33m    TOOLS\u001b[39m\u001b[90m ─────────────────────┐\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • Static analysis tools do not detect main-thread blockin...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • CI pipeline has no performance regression benchmarks fo...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[67.396779, "o", "\u001b[90m                              ┌─────────────────────── \u001b[39m\u001b[33mENVIRONMENT\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • Lab testing uses simulated GPS at 60 km/h (real issue m...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • Test routes do not include missed-exit scenarios\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[67.998581, "o", "\u001b[33m    MATERIALS\u001b[39m\u001b[90m ─────────────────────┐\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • iDrive 7 route engine assumes single-threaded execution...\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      • HERE Maps SDK v3 route API is synchronous by design\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[68.59985, "o", "\u001b[90m                              ┌─────────────────────── \u001b[39m\u001b[33mMEASUREMENT\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • No telemetry for route recalculation latency in production\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │  • Crash reports do not capture thread state at time of hang\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m                              │\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[71.203775, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m  ═══ ROOT CAUSE REPORT ═══\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[71.204337, "o", "\u001b[36m┌──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mRoot Cause ID\u001b[22m\u001b[39m        \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[33mROOT-042\u001b[39m                                                 \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mCategory\u001b[22m\u001b[39m             \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37mDESIGN\u001b[39m                                                   \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mConfidence\u001b[22m\u001b[39m           \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32m████████████████████████████\u001b[39m\u001b[90m░░\u001b[39m 92%                       \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mSummary\u001b[22m\u001b[39m              \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37mSynchronous route recalculation engine blocking HMI mai\u001b[39m… \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mAffected Defects\u001b[22m\u001b[39m     \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37mDEF-3901, DEF-4512, DEF-4822, DEF-4823\u001b[39m                   \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m└──────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[72.406231, "o", "\u001b[37m\u001b[1m  Detailed Analysis:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[72.406262, "o", "\u001b[90m    The iDrive 7 navigation route engine executes route recalculation \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    synchronously on the main HMI thread. During the iDrive 8 migration, this \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    module was ported without architectural changes due to its \"low-change\" \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    classification. At highway speeds (>120 km/h), missed-exit recalculations \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    involve significantly more graph traversal than urban rerouting, causing \u001b[39m\r\n"]
[72.406332, "o", "\u001b[90m    8-12 second UI freezes. The absence of threading model validation in the \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    migration review process allowed this architectural debt to reach \u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    production. \u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[73.606807, "o", "\u001b[32m\u001b[1m  ✓ Preventive Measures:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[74.208937, "o", "\u001b[32m    1. \u001b[39m\u001b[37mMove route recalculation to dedicated worker thread with async callback to UI\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[74.809872, "o", "\u001b[32m    2. \u001b[39m\u001b[37mAdd threading model validation step to platform migration review checklist\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[75.410728, "o", "\u001b[32m    3. \u001b[39m\u001b[37mImplement route recalculation latency telemetry (P50/P95/P99) in production\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[76.010949, "o", "\u001b[32m    4. \u001b[39m\u001b[37mAdd high-speed missed-exit scenarios to navigation integration test suite\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[76.611932, "o", "\u001b[32m    5. \u001b[39m\u001b[37mSet performance budget: route recalculation must complete within 2 seconds\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[76.611971, "o", "\r\n"]
[77.814128, "o", "\u001b[33m\u001b[1m  ⚡ Related Patterns Discovered:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[77.814189, "o", "\u001b[33m    • Synchronous-to-async migration debt\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      3 occurrences across: Navigation, Voice Control, Media Player\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[33m    • Missing performance validation in platform migration\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m      5 occurrences across: HMI, Connectivity, ADAS Visualization\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[80.818138, "o", "\r\n\u001b[90m──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m  ═══ DEMO SUMMARY ═══\u001b[22m\u001b[39m"]
[80.818167, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[80.819764, "o", "\u001b[36m┌────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┬──────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┬────────────────────────────┐\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mCapability\u001b[22m\u001b[39m             \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mWhat AI Does\u001b[22m\u001b[39m                 \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[37m\u001b[1mKey Benefit\u001b[22m\u001b[39m                \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[36mDefect Quality Check\u001b[39m   \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m Validates mandatory fields   \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32mReject 12% → Accept 92%\u001b[39m    \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m                        \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m against configurable rules   \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32mquality score\u001b[39m              \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[36mDuplicate Detection\u001b[39m    \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m Semantic similarity via      \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32mCaught 94% match that\u001b[39m      \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m                        \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m vector embeddings (not keyw… \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32mkeyword search missed\u001b[39m      \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m├────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼──────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┼────────────────────────────┤\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[36mRoot Cause Analysis\u001b[39m    \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m Descriptions + comments +    \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32m92% confidence RCA\u001b[39m         \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m                        \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m historical patterns analyzed \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m \u001b[32m+ 5 preventive measures\u001b[39m    \u001b[36m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m└────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┴──────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\u001b[36m┴────────────────────────────┘\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[37m\u001b[1m  What Sets AQE Apart:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    • Understands meaning, not just keywords — catches duplicates others miss\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[80.819783, "o", "\u001b[90m    • Learns from historical defect patterns to predict future risks\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    • Multi-method RCA that traces symptoms to systemic root causes\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    • Configurable quality gates that enforce your org's defect standards\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    • Analyzes descriptions, comments, and resolution history together\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[80.819854, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m    Powered by Agentic Quality Engineering (AQE) Framework\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m    https://agentic-qe.dev\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n\u001b[90m──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[80.820077, "o", "\u001b[?25h"]
